## Icon PNG Banane Ka Tarika

**Free tool:** https://cloudconvert.com/svg-to-png

Steps:
1. `icon.svg` upload karo
2. Width: **192**, Height: **192** → Convert → Download → naam rakho `icon-192.png`
3. Dobara upload karo Width: **512**, Height: **512** → Convert → Download → naam rakho `icon-512.png`

