## Final Folder Structure
```
potentialdashboard/
├── index.html      ← modified (head + body changes)
├── manifest.json   ← new file
├── sw.js           ← new file
└── icons/
    ├── icon.svg    ← new file
    ├── icon-192.png ← convert karke add karo
    └── icon-512.png ← convert karke add karo
```

